Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_enable...register_limit(25.10)    timing_enable...register_limit(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_genclk_source_path_register_limit

Syntax
       timing_enable_genclk_source_path_register_limit

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Limits  the  generated clock source latency path to traverse across one
       register only.

       When set to false, the software allows master  clock  latency  path  to
       traverse across any number of sequential devices to reach the generated
       clock target pin.

       When  set to true, the software restricts the master clock latency path
       for a generated clock to traverse exactly one sequential device.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

